<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <title>My application</title>
</head>
<body>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<div  style="background-color:RGB(223, 207, 190);">
    <div class="container">
        <br>
        <br>
        <h1>Subarray of size k with given sum</h1>
        <p>Write an array arr[], an integer K and a Sum. The task is to check if there exists any subarray with K elements whose sum is equal to the given sum.
             If any of the subarray with size K has the sum equal to the given sum then result is True otherwise result is False.</p>        

       <br>
       <p style="font-size:20px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
       font-weight:bold; width: 300px; height:50px;  border-radius: 100% 100% 100% 100%;
       background-color: rgba(255, 128, 0, 0.842);">Result is {{result}}</p>
       
        <form action="compute" method="post">
            <div class="row  bg-light pb-4 mb-5">
            
                <div class = "col-sm-3 mt-3">
                    
                    <textarea name="input1" rows="10" cols="30"></textarea>
                    <p> Enter array to this part. write one element per line. Ex: 
                        4
                        2
                        10
                        2
                        3
                        20
                        12
                        7
                        9</p>
                </div>
                <div class = "col-sm-1"></div>
                <div class = "col-sm-3 mt-3">
                    <textarea name="input2" rows="3" cols="25"></textarea>
                    <p>Enter the K value. The K value specifies the number of elements in the subarray.
                        Just enter 1 number. Do not leave this field blank! Ex: 4
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class = "col-sm-1"></div>
                <div class = "col-sm-3 mt-3">
                    <textarea name="input3" rows="3" cols="25"></textarea>
                    <p>Enter the Sum value. The Sum value is sum of the searched subarray.
                        Just enter 1 number. Do not leave this field blank! Ex: 18
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class = "col-sm-1"></div>
            <br>
            <br>
            
            <div class="text-center">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-warning" >Send</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
</div>
</body>
</html>


